ca.wise.api.output

Enum GlobalStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GlobalStatistics>
      • ca.wise.api.output.GlobalStatistics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GlobalStatistics>

    public enum GlobalStatistics
extends Enum<GlobalStatistics>
    All supported statistics values that can be used across the API. Not all locations will support all statistics.
